  "title": "Sales Specialist, Omnichannel Messaging",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a leading telecom organization to hire a Sales Specialist, Omnichannel Messaging to drive adoption and revenue growth of omnichannel and CPaaS solutions across Government and Enterprise sectors.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Drive new logo acquisition and grow existing enterprise and government accounts</li><li>Achieve and exceed sales targets for Omnichannel, RCS and SMS solutions</li><li>Build and manage a strong sales pipeline with accurate forecasting</li><li>Identify opportunities in authentication, fraud prevention, customer service and engagement use cases</li><li>Help clients move from basic SMS to modern omnichannel workflows (SMS, WhatsApp, RCS)</li><li>Lead end-to-end sales cycles, working with internal teams and vendor partners</li><li>Influence key stakeholders across business, IT and procurement</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>5+ years of B2B sales experience, preferably in CPaaS, MarTech or telecom</li><li>Strong track record in closing large enterprise deals and growing key accounts</li><li>Experience managing long sales cycles with multiple stakeholders</li><li>Exposure to public sector procurement and tender processes</li><li>Good understanding of CPaaS and messaging ecosystem</li><li>Strong consultative selling, negotiation and stakeholder management skills</li><li>Self-driven, resilient and results-oriented</li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 5,
